{"tid":1213123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因應警方要求，金鐘站今早將會關閉，荃灣綫，港島綫及南港島綫的列車將不停金鐘站","createTime":"2019-06-13T00:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T00:43:15.000Z","uid":137493,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4e18b4eaa7b24efa64fd79a382bb9f0c29e6cd32","tid":1213123,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:35:10.000Z","msg":"服務受阻 Service Disruption<br />\n<br />\n因應警方要求，金鐘站今早將會關閉，荃灣綫，港島綫及南港島綫的列車將不停金鐘站<br />\nAs requested by police, Admiralty Station will be temporarily closed, trains running on the Tsuen Wan Line, Island Line and South Island Line will not stop at Admiralty Station<br />\n<br />\n列車班次受影響Train frequency affected<br />\n<br />\n荃灣綫部分路段仍維持列車服務，但班次或會受到影響。請為行程預留充裕時間。<br />\nTrain service is still operating between some locations on the Tsuen Wan Line. However, train frequency may be subject to change. Please allow more time for travel."},{"pid":"f57765ff8d2aed71bc78f6d0405f1bf0208dd4b6","tid":1213123,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:36:09.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"ae044e7e53de0faa11e0cb69739664b568a44f18","tid":1213123,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:36:22.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"adfee38116aa18f7e3cec5a60c66eff582de068e","tid":1213123,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:36:35.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"13205900d881b017b2eba6555157fc915387533e","tid":1213123,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:36:48.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"75163676f355c6b9e522d1fea7fa5a797e31c2b9","tid":1213123,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:37:02.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"d04089126ca4e6cc1a30c3a0778796ecf1dd9d70","tid":1213123,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"578ca392c3e8404670cf93952641275a9cd64c60","tid